author: Warhammer
description:
Raise the dead to fight for you with the power of necromancy! Pre-order the Soulblight Gravelords: Deathrattle boxed set next week and BOOM – your very own skeletal soldiery. Plus there’s a whole raft of (s)elf-assuredly superior reinforcements on their way for the High Elf Realms too.

On Wednesday, the Blacktalons are tested to their limits when a dark threat erupts from Hammerhal's sundered Realmgate in the mid-season finale of Blacktalon on Warhammer TV, alongside new episodes of Loremasters, Citadel Colour Masterclass, and more.
